<note id="fs-id1167066997945" class="os-teacher">
<title>Teacher Support</title>
<para id="fs-id1167066833382">Explain that it is very exciting when a prediction of relativity theory is tested successfully. Some of the predictions were in doubt because they sounded so bizarre.</para>
