</m:math> . An object’s mass is constant. Call acceleration due to gravity on Mars <emphasis>g</emphasis><emphasis effect="italics"><sub>M</sub></emphasis> and weight on Mars <emphasis>W</emphasis><emphasis effect="italics"><sub>M</sub></emphasis>.</para></note>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167067042581">
<label/>
<title>Solution</title>
